QuestData.Title: We're Going To Be Friends
QuestData.Description:
It is going to be fun getting to know you. You're not half bad!
We kinda got a little gift for you, to welcome you to the neighborhood.
I hope Atolia was able to put together something neat, she didn't have much time.
QuestData.LogDescription: Visit Atolia Seapearl, in Newhome, for your gift.
